                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.41/104.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">El Paso</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-02-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 21, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I to-day requested Villa to order Benton’s body delivered to wife. Have no answer
                    yet. I omitted mention to-day’s telegram that I have known both Banda and Farias
                    several years, their testimony deserves credence.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">G. C. Carothers</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
